10 REM DMA SETUP FILL THE WHOLE SCREEN
15 poke 53345, 0: REM RESET DMA SIZE (8BIT)
20 POKE 53346, 255: REM SOURCE ADDRESS LOW BYTE
30 POKE 53347, 223: REM SOURCE ADDRESS HIGH BYTE
60 POKE 53350, 0: REM DESTINATION ADDRESS LOW BYTE
70 POKE 53351, 4: REM DESTINATION ADDRESS HIGH BYTE
100 POKE 53354, 232: REM TRANSFER SIZE LOW BYTE
110 POKE 53355, 3: REM TRANSFER SIZE HIGH BYTE
120 POKE 53356, 0: REM READ INCREMENT
130 POKE 53357, 1: REM WRITE INCREMENT
140 POKE 53354, 232: REM TRANSFER SIZE LOW BYTE
150 POKE 53355, 3: REM TRANSFER SIZE HIGH BYTE
160 POKE 53344, 1: REM START DMA TRANSFER
170 PRINT "DMA TRANSFER STARTED"
